{"word":"Constancy","slug":"constancy","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Constancy</b> In obedience<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=119&verse=31'>Psa 119:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=119&verse=33'>Psa 119:33</a><br/> In friendship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=27&verse=10'>Pro 27:10</a><br/> Under suffering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=5&verse=12'>Mat 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=5'>Heb 12:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=4&verse=16'>1Pe 4:16</a><br/> In prayer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=1'>Luk 18:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=12&verse=12'>Rom 12:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=6&verse=18'>Eph 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=2'>Col 4:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=17'>1Th 5:17</a><br/> In beneficence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=9'>Gal 6:9</a><br/> In profession<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=10&verse=23'>Heb 10:23</a><br/> Instances of:<br/> - Ruth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=14'>Rth 1:14</a> <br/> - Jonathan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=1'>1Sa 18:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=20&verse=16'>1Sa 20:16</a> <br/> - Priscilla and Aquila<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=16&verse=4'>Rom 16:4</a><br/><a href='S:Character'>Character</a>; <a href='S:Stability'>Stability</a> "}]}